Nael – Emacs major mode for Lean
********************************

Nael is a package for GNU Emacs (https://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/)
that provides a major mode for Lean (https://lean-lang.org/) language.
“Nael” reversed is “Lean” and ends in “el” as in Emacs-Lisp.

